:09.000Z","msg":"&middot;-&middot;"},{"pid":"014b86e7512c8ed030bec4776a005b2d022d334c","tid":483303,"uid":160626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>懷疑返佢當打和啦 super</blockquote><br />\n冇咁得閑"},{"pid":"fdc9d5e5634fd7e0cc6e033fec0e413e8ab4566e","tid":483303,"uid":126760,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街點解可以咁撚幽默？"},{"pid":"d099ddc5f6795ae165b793ea5b14f89c800cf1ed","tid":483303,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T04:46:27.000Z","msg":"收埋隻右手佢"},{"pid":"e7c99ac4e0044e3542dd649d856fd5a38cd51f0e","tid":483303,"uid":154773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T05:23:58.000Z","msg":"我都成日會懷疑男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但其實應該係我自己諗多左"},{"pid":"7302d080f130c8b488d7e3ec6b17d1afe0d7cdd8","tid":483303,"uid":58983,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:34:09.000Z","msg":"因為你女朋友自己出左軌，所以一見你有咩証狀，就覺得你同佢一樣出軌。實際就係死港女比撚完帽你帶就自己內疚屈你出軌等自己好過。"},{"pid":"ee22885f1d00e8cc76365e3b9d8d25a5234435d0","tid":483303,"uid":31887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你女朋友自己出左軌，所以一見你有咩証狀，就覺得你同佢一樣出軌。實際就係死港女比撚完帽你帶就自己內疚屈你出軌等自己好過。</blockquote><br />\n同意<br />\n我分手前 條女都係咁屈我<br />\n明明所有時間陪佢<br />\n手機 同 acc佢掌控<br />\n<br />\n最後分手有一日我搵佢朋友<br />\n佢朋友唔小心爆響口話佢有幾張sim卡<br />\n我仲見到佢show比我睇另一個number<br />\n<br />\n如果你無咩行為比人值得懷疑 而佢堅持屈你<br />\n好大機會係佢出左軌先<br />\n見到同樣線索 杯弓蛇影/驚報應"},{"pid":"1f37ffc3ec21fee0808c0073a0dcddc299aec5cb","tid":483303,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"小心啦 通常身有屎先會反客為主"},{"pid":"a75da3f42cb0d9953c1d73482b60817a4ed0421b","tid":483303,"uid":160626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T21:05: